    <abstract>
      <t>This memo specifies requirements for a framework and protocols for accessing and updating Internet Media Guide (IMG) information for media-on-demand and multicast applications.  These requirements are designed to guide choice and development of IMG protocols for efficient and scalable delivery.  This memo provides information for the Internet community.
	 </t>
